TRI-CITY FREIGHT LINES CORPORATION v. J. E. YEATTS. [No. 24,

October Term, 1935.]

Decided November 1st, 1935.

The cause was submitted on brief to Bond, C. J., IJrner, Offutt, Parke, Sloan, Mitchell,, Shehan, and Johnson. JJ.

Joseph W. Spector, Joseph O. Buchoff, Abraham Rostov, and Symone S. Spector, for the appellant. Urner, J.,

delivered the opinion of the Court.
